    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and light wear on the interior upholstery, the car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It offers a great balance of reliability and value for anyone looking for a solid, pre-owned vehicle.",
