      "description": "Presenting an exceptional acquisition for the discerning collector: a vehicle maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic integrity, from its mirror-finish exterior to a meticulously preserved interior environment. Every mechanical component has been curated to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state. We invite you to inspect this benchmark of automotive excellence, where pristine condition meets unparalleled sophistication.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
